title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 141-3.6 - Nonresident janitor
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 141-3.6 - Nonresident janitor

State Regulations
A
nonresident janitor
is a janitor as
defined above who does not reside in the building where he or she renders
services, or in another building within a distance of 200 feet
therefrom. Notes
